'print' method for Dataset objects

Source: R/Dataset.R
print.Dataset.Rd

Print a Dataset object

# S3 method for Dataset
print(x, ...)

Arguments

x

A Dataset object

...

Additional arguments

Examples

cars.data <- Dataset(data = cars, target = "dist")
print(cars.data)
